  "commonDecision": "Promote reset/H10 command planning before sync error handling; H10 query failures and reset notification failures are shared transport-error propagation, while sync failure terminals remain platform compatibility gates.",
  "notes": "Android and iOS agree on the command/query IDs, H10 query failure propagation, reset payload flags, and reset notification failure propagation. Sync start and stop error handling intentionally differs today, so the KMP migration must keep this vector as a decision gate rather than silently choosing one platform behavior."
